{"tid":2420195,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"城大作新校歌｜由校長郭位填詞，鼓勵師生專注教學及研究","createTime":"2021-02-23T18:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T18:51:53.000Z","uid":312744,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"172e99939ce991f241ae107832a6a949ad959855","tid":2420195,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"城市大學為加強學校品牌定位，將推出由校長郭位填詞、專業作曲家李峻一作曲的新校歌，希望令大學專注於學術和研究合一，尊重多元文化，做到和而不同。校歌亦有廣東話改編版。<br />\n校歌以「學研出塵」為主題，展現大學的教學理念、特色，及對學生與教職員的期望和鼓勵。「多元文化」一直是大學致力推動的教研環境，各方見解縱有不同，但能互相尊重，彼此切磋，從而促進創意與思考，昂然邁向未知的知識領域。<br />\n歌詞中一句「大問於市，學研出塵」是表達對城大人的期望，校歌寄語學生及學者應追求卓越，心繫世界，專注教學和研究，以知識「引領世界」，為香港以至全球作貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E6%A0%A1%E6%AD%8C%EF%BD%9C%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%83%AD%E4%BD%8D%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E3%80%80%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%88%E6%B3%A8%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-256834?fbclid=IwAR0a8AxunjfoH35tQPQFjs_ZKxJkIKXGXjTiiKRlZ0f4pGOIXtDeYX5c5C4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%25AD%258C%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%2583%25AD%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A9%259E%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-256834%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0a8AxunjfoH35tQPQFjs_ZKxJkIKXGXjTiiKRlZ0f4pGOIXtDeYX5c5C4&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm1Fonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=b76d0ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E6%A0%A1%E6%AD%8C%EF%BD%9C%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%83%AD%E4%BD%8D%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E3%80%80%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%88%E6%B3%A8%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-256834?fbclid=IwAR0a8AxunjfoH35tQPQFjs_ZKxJkIKXGXjTii